N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1211.52 - Class B explosives

State Regulations

No vehicle shall enter either a tunnel, the George

Washington Bridge Lower Level or George Washington Bridge Expressway if its
load includes any Class B explosives except special fireworks (including
railway or track torpedoes) not in excess of 10 pounds gross weight per
vehicle. Notes
